      "gains": "Delivery service stays fast and unaffected by provider outages. Retries are structural (queue-native) not hand-rolled. Adding channels requires zero changes to delivery service. Failed notifications are captured in DLQ, never silently lost. Temporal decoupling matches the 5-minute latency budget perfectly.",
