    "patterns_to_follow": "Use a Result type (not thrown exceptions) for adapter responses so the worker can make retry/DLQ decisions explicitly. Keep adapters stateless and independently testable. Use dependency injection for the adapter registry so tests can swap in fakes. Log every state transition with correlationId. Use structured JSON logging.",
